  "final_answer": "For fever relief, honey is a traditional ingredient that may help. According to the Hadith, the Prophet Muhammad (SAWW) advised cooling fever with water, and some narrations specifically mention Zamzam water. As Narrated by Abu Jamra Ad-Dabi (RA) and Aisha (RA), the Prophet (SAWW) said, \"Fever is from the heat of the (Hell) Fire, so cool it with water.\" While honey is not directly mentioned in these Hadiths as a cure for fever, its potential health benefits make it a noteworthy ingredient. However, it's essential to consult a healthcare professional before using any remedies, especially if you have a severe or persistent fever.",
